title: Halo Screensaver
description:
Download and Enjoy Halo Screensaver

What can be said today of the Halo saga that has not been said already. We fought the Covenant for survival of the universe, with an extensive arsenal of weapons against all kinds of creatures and breathtaking scenery. With this screensaver will enjoy three powerful animations that perfectly reflected the strength of the halo universe, with the soundtrack we all know.


==================================================================

OS: Windows 8, 7, Vista, 2003, XP, 2000, 98, Me, NT

Howto Install Screensavers/Animated Wallpapers On Windows Vista / 7 / 8
Right-click in the program installer, and then click Run As Administrator

Enjoy!
